snippet.title: Mono - Story 2: The Monster Within | TEASER TRAILER 1
snippet.description:
Mono is available on steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/611640?beta=1



Story 2 of Mono will take us into the depths of the Dev's computer. To once and for all destroy all of his creations, but the dev himself seems to be in conflict with someone or something. Find out what Q2 of 2017 in Mono Story 2 - The Monster Within
